"""Test find_host_lun_id_for_vol unsuccessful return."""
with mock.patch.object(self.provisioning, 'get_maskingview_connections',
    side_effect=[list(), [{'not_host_lun': 'value'}]]):
    for x in range(0, 2):
        host_lun_id2 = self.provisioning.find_host_lun_id_for_vol(self.data
            .masking_view_name_f, self.data.device_id)
        self.assertIsNone(host_lun_id2)
